high_descs: Turn around and go straight, to the dresser.
Pick up the cell phone on the dresser, to the left of the credit card.
Turn around, move forward, turn right, then turn right to face the dresser.
Put the cell phone in the bottom right dresser drawer.
Move forward to the dresser.
Pick up the cell phone, to the right of the pencil.
Turn around, move forward, turn right, then turn right to face the dresser.
Put the cell phone in the bottom right dresser drawer, to the right of the other cell phone.
anns.task_desc: Put two cell phones in the drawer.

high_descs: Cross the room to stand in front of the dresser that's by the window.
Pick the cell phone up from on top of the dresser.
Carry the cell phone a few steps away from the dresser.
Open the bottom right drawer of the dresser and place the phone inside and close the door.
Move closer to the dresser.
Pick up the cell phone that's to the right of the pencil.
Carry the phone a few steps back away from the dresser again, so you have room to open a drawer.
Open the bottom right drawer, and place the phone inside next to the other phone.
anns.task_desc: Move two cell phones to a drawer in the dresser.
